24 - 30 people, you will be hard pressed after the first hour.  My current guild has averaged 30 - 40 with around 50 being the highest count and we failed, just not enough tankage.<br />
<br />
Like you, the most successful raids I have seen are with 70+ people.  That seems to still be the magic number.  This is still a situation where numbers are more important than levels.<br />
<br />
Send me a tell and I can see if I can muster some folks for ya.</div>
