I have been looking into either the War Crested Ring and/or the Anger of Druzzil &amp; Improved Damage II augs lately and it got me wondering...<br />
<br />
I checked out Lucy for the specs on both and ran some queries through my local database o' spells and came up with this:<br />
(Disclaimer: Info in my database might not be up to date and according to LUCY there is no resist check on WCR's ID4 focus).<br />
These are, from what I gather, our spells that work with their respective focus:<br /><ul><li><br />
<b>Improved Damage IV (War Crested Ring)</b><br />
65 Aura of Hate<br />
65 Touch of Innoruuk<br />
64 Spear of Decay<br />
64 Scythe of Innoruuk<br />
63 Aura of Pain<br />
62 Touch of Volatis<br />
62 Zevfeer's Bite<br />
62 Deny Undead<br />
60 Drain Soul<br />
57 Drain Spirit<br />
55 Spirit Tap<br />
55 Expel Undead<br />
54 Spear of Plague<br />
54 Scythe of Death<br />
51 Siphon Life<br />
49 Dismiss Undead<br />
49 Life Leech<br />
49 Spear of Pain<br />
49 Scythe of Darkness<br />
39 Expulse Undead<br />
34 Spear of Disease<br />
30 Lifedraw<br />
22 Ward Undead<br />
15 Lifespike<br />
09 Lifetap<br />
1 Harm Touch<br />
<br />
<b>Anger of Druzzil (Gleaming Prism of Destruction augment)</b><br />
65 Touch of Innoruuk<br />
64 Scythe of Innoruuk<br />
62 Touch of Volatis<br />
62 Deny Undead<br />
60 Drain Soul<br />
57 Drain Spirit<br />
55 Spirit Tap<br />
55 Expel Undead<br />
54 Scythe of Death<br />
51 Siphon Life<br />
49 Dismiss Undead<br />
49 Life Leech<br />
49 Scythe of Darkness<br />
39 Expulse Undead<br />
30 Lifedraw<br />
22 Ward Undead<br />
15 Lifespike<br />
09 Lifetap<br />
<br />
<b>Improved Damage II (Cracked Limestone of Aggression augment)</b><br />
34 Spear of Disease<br />
1 Harm Touch</li></ul>Looking at this, it would appear that removing the War Crested Ring and instead having the Anger of Druzzil &amp; IDII augs you <i>no longer</i> gain focus'ed benefit from:<ul><li><br />
65 Aura of Hate<br />
64 Spear of Decay<br />
63 Aura of Pain<br />
62 Zevfeer's Bite<br />
54 Spear of Plague<br />
49 Spear of Pain</li></ul><br />
At least I think I got that right. <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" class="inlineimg" /></div>
